<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT88">
<l>uyirkoṇ ṭuṭaloḻiya vōṭumpō tōṭi</l>
<l>yayarveṉṟa tīrppāṉpēr pāṭi ceyaltīrac</l>
<l>cintittu vāḻvārē vāḻvār ciṟucamayap</l>
<l>pantaṉaiyār vāḻvēl paḻutu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is only those who sing the names of [the Lord]—who ends pain,</l>
<l rend="indent">Running after [the souls] when [they] run away taking the[ir] life-breath</l>
<l rend="indent">[with them], leaving behind [their] bodies—</l>
<l>And who contemplate so that actions cease</l>
<l>who [reach] felicity.</l>
<l>As for the lives of those with bondages [linked to] petty creeds,</l>
<l>They are unprofitable.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
